# ADARA "Fix ITEMS" Script...! ;-O
#
# At present, changing ITEMS Sample ID numbers when Re-Translating a Run
# is *Very* Precarious and Fraught with Peril, so NEVER USE THIS, Lol. ;-D
#
# Seriously though, you can do this, but it requires applying a very
# in-depth manual hands-on procedure/recipe per Run, including capturing
# and inserting a series of several dozen binary data packets (it's not
# _Just_ the Sample ID, but *All* 42 of the associated Sample Meta-Data
# PVs, too! ;-D), as harvested from some _Other_ existing Run's Raw Data,
# that already had the given ITEMS Sample ID selected, so all the
# Meta-Data fields have already been populated and binary data packets
# generated. I don't have any automated tools to query the ITEMS
# database or fabricate the ADARA binary stream packets, from outside of
# the production ADARA server software.
#
# This preliminary Script is to Automate Changing the ITEMS Sample ID for
# Run(s) and Resubmitting Them Through the STC to Re-Catalog...! ;-D
#
# (Because it can happen that often... ;-)
#
# This current version is based on the latest accumulated knowledge
# from manually fixing several series of Runs with the Wrong ITEMS
# Sample ID Meta-Data on NOMAD and POWGEN.
#
# I Wish You Good Luck and God's Speed...! ;-D
#
#    Jeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeem :)
#

